$ Oracle: Init parameter RECYCLEBIN
@ recyclebin

The value of the → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters[init parameter] `recyclebin` can be set to `on` or `off`.

If the value is set to `on`, dropping a table «moves» the table to the *recycle bin* where they can be recovered again.

sa:

 `→ development/databases/Oracle/installed/data-dictionary/recyclebin`

 The SQL verb `→ development/databases/Oracle/SQL/statement/verbs/purge`.

  → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters
